{"id":29017314195,"name":"Run api tests","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGwZETkw","head_branch":"perf-getmetadata-oug-member-count-2.42.5.1","head_sha":"c65ab1d0c685c15e7e8059e87a2128005f813d62","path":".github/workflows/run-api-tests.yml","run_number":50981,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"perf: avoid loading org unit group members for OUG{} indicator counts (2.42.5.1)","status":"completed","conclusion":"success","workflow_id":5591308,"check_suite_id":78489764233,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAASRlrBiQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195","pull_requests":[{"id":4021813793,"number":24402,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/pulls/24402","head":{"ref":"perf-getmetadata-oug-member-count-2.42.5.1","sha":"c65ab1d0c685c15e7e8059e87a2128005f813d62","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}},"base":{"ref":"patch/2.42.5.1","sha":"9d7f88a940e6e5ee766767424306fb11cb4a1f2b","repo":{"id":66940520,"name":"dhis2-core","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core"}}}],"created_at":"2026-07-09T12:11:29Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T12:27:21Z","run_started_at":"2026-07-09T12:11:29Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/78489764233","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/29017314195/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"perf: avoid loading org unit group members for OUG{} indicator counts (#24260)\n\n* perf: avoid loading org unit group members for OUG{} indicator counts\n\nsubstituteIndicatorExpressions (called on every dhis-web-dataentry getMetaData request) resolved each OUG{uid} indicator reference via group.getMembers().size(), which initialises the entire org unit group members collection - on a large instance, 70k+ OrganisationUnit entities hydrated into the session per request.\n\nThis dominated getMetaData: a ~5s floor and spikes to 14-22s, from the members load, a single-OU rehydration N+1 when the entity cache was cold, and commit-time dirty-checking of the hydrated entities (~2GB allocated per request). Measured floor on a large production instance dropped from ~5.2s to ~0.2s.\n\nResolve the count with a count subquery instead: new OrganisationUnitGroupStore.getOrganisationUnitGroupMemberCounts(uids) uses HQL size(g.members), which never initialises the collection; substituteIndicatorExpressions looks up only the referenced groups and substitutes counts directly.\n\nAlso mark substituteIndicatorExpressions @Transactional(readOnly = true): it only mutates the transient Indicator.exploded* display fields, so it never writes; readOnly sets flush mode MANUAL as a guard against dirty-checking.\n\nBehaviour preserved: the count is the global group membership total, as before. The runtime, org-unit-scoped OUG{} count used in analytics is a separate path via orgUnitCountMap.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* test: assert OUG{} substitution output is unchanged end-to-end\n\nIntegration test exercising the real substituteIndicatorExpressions against Postgres: asserts the exploded numerator/denominator equal String.valueOf(group.getMembers().size()) - i.e. byte-identical to the pre-change behaviour - while the count now comes from the count query.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* refactor: address SonarQube smells in OUG count fix\n\n- collect referenced org unit group UIDs with a stream instead of a separate loop, leaving a single loop over indicators (keeps the single batched count query)\n\n- drop redundant Mockito eq() matcher in the substitution unit test\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n* docs: reword OUG count comment to avoid SonarQube commented-code false positive\n\njava:S125 flagged the explanatory comment as commented-out code because it contained code-like tokens (method-call and brace syntax). Reworded as plain prose; no behaviour change.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\n\n---------\n\nCo-authored-by: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Jason Pickering","email":"jason@dhis2.org"},"id":"c65ab1d0c685c15e7e8059e87a2128005f813d62","tree_id":"194cf635190fad69cd394a7539161891fd0247d3","timestamp":"2026-07-09T12:07:42Z","committer":{"name":"Enrico","email":"enrico@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhi